WEBVTT

00:11.080 --> 00:12.190
-What are you doing?
-You want to fight?

00:11.130 --> 00:14.990
[Peace at the border]

00:12.190 --> 00:13.030
What's your problem?

00:13.030 --> 00:13.720
Let go!

00:13.750 --> 00:14.240
Say that again?

00:14.240 --> 00:15.100
All right, all right.

00:15.100 --> 00:15.750
-Say that again!
-Back off!

00:15.750 --> 00:16.550
Think I'm scared of you?

00:16.550 --> 00:17.390
That's enough!

00:17.390 --> 00:17.920
Back off!

00:18.730 --> 00:19.760
Let them go.

00:20.800 --> 00:22.050
Those war prisoners

00:21.460 --> 00:27.730
[Peace at the border]

00:22.230 --> 00:24.440
were captured by our Yanzhou Army
with blood and sweat.

00:24.440 --> 00:25.510
Why should you Jizhou Army

00:25.510 --> 00:26.480
get half of them?

00:26.480 --> 00:27.920
-Exactly!
-Why?

00:28.230 --> 00:29.120
Why?

00:29.440 --> 00:32.390
Commandant Fan
and our Discipline Inspector are in love.

00:32.390 --> 00:32.750
Yeah!

00:32.750 --> 00:34.520
They'll be family soon.

00:34.790 --> 00:36.350
Never mind half,

00:36.840 --> 00:38.710
even giving them all to the Jizhou Army

00:38.710 --> 00:40.200
would be only right!

00:40.200 --> 00:41.280
Exactly. It's only right!

00:41.280 --> 00:42.640
Shut up! Shut up!

00:43.280 --> 00:44.880
What nonsense are you spouting?

00:44.880 --> 00:47.010
Commandant Fan already has a husband.

00:47.200 --> 00:48.960
Why would she have anything to do

00:48.960 --> 00:50.200
with Discipline Inspector Li
behind his back?

00:50.200 --> 00:51.000
Bullshit!

00:51.510 --> 00:52.920
Commandant Fan's husband

00:52.920 --> 00:54.640
died in battle long ago.

00:55.200 --> 00:56.670
Even if he hadn't,

00:56.840 --> 00:59.670
how could he compare
to our Discipline Inspector?

00:59.750 --> 01:01.000
That's right!

01:01.000 --> 01:01.470
Not at all!

01:01.470 --> 01:02.790
Isn't your Discipline Inspector Li

01:02.790 --> 01:04.430
marrying the Princess Royal?

01:04.430 --> 01:06.790
Why is he still entangled
with Commandant Fan?

01:06.790 --> 01:07.680
Exactly!

01:07.680 --> 01:09.039
None of your damn business.

01:09.039 --> 01:10.870
Our Discipline Inspector
goes to see Commandant Fan every day.

01:10.870 --> 01:11.680
Don't you see?

01:11.680 --> 01:13.200
As for you,

01:13.200 --> 01:14.840
don't tell me your Lord

01:15.320 --> 01:16.970
has also taken a fancy to Commandant Fan?

01:16.970 --> 01:17.560
Nonsense!

01:17.560 --> 01:18.950
-What did you say?
-Don't think so?

01:18.950 --> 01:20.550
-Hit me!
-What are you doing?

01:21.120 --> 01:21.680
Stop!

01:21.810 --> 01:22.420
Let go!

01:21.850 --> 01:27.440
[Peace at the border]

01:22.460 --> 01:22.789
Come on!

01:22.789 --> 01:23.550
Watch it!

01:25.950 --> 01:27.610
We are all brothers-in-arms.

01:28.070 --> 01:30.800
Yet you fight
and hurt each other over prisoners.

01:30.840 --> 01:32.750
Where is your military discipline?

01:32.750 --> 01:33.479
Lord Li.

01:33.900 --> 01:35.020
You be the judge.

01:35.400 --> 01:37.800
You and Commandant Fan
will be family soon.

01:38.350 --> 01:39.680
There's no need
to distinguish these military merits

01:39.680 --> 01:40.950
so clearly.

01:41.200 --> 01:41.950
Insolence!

01:42.950 --> 01:45.030
How can you spread such gossip?

01:45.120 --> 01:47.479
I don't care if Discipline Inspector Li
likes Commandant Fan,

01:47.479 --> 01:49.640
but to take
our Yanzhou Emperor Bodyguards' merits

01:49.640 --> 01:50.590
is not acceptable.

01:50.590 --> 01:51.120
Right?

01:51.120 --> 01:52.000
What now?

01:52.000 --> 01:52.950
You got a problem?

01:52.490 --> 01:54.430
[Peace at the border]

01:54.560 --> 01:55.780
Attention, generals!

01:55.340 --> 01:56.420
[Commanding Token]

01:59.759 --> 02:01.790
I met Mrs. Fan when we were humble.

02:02.040 --> 02:03.560
Just like all of you,

02:04.070 --> 02:06.640
we share a bond of fighting side by side
through life and death situations.

02:06.640 --> 02:07.400
Now,

02:07.920 --> 02:10.650
Commandant Fan and I
have become sworn siblings.

02:11.360 --> 02:12.160
In the future,

02:12.680 --> 02:14.540
I will be treating her as a sister.

02:15.710 --> 02:19.120
If anyone gossips
and stirs up trouble again,

02:19.710 --> 02:22.030
or slanders Commandant Fan's reputation,

02:22.030 --> 02:23.520
they will receive 30 strokes
of the military staff.

02:23.520 --> 02:24.720
Let this be a warning!

02:24.800 --> 02:26.000
-Yes, Sir!
-Yes, Sir!

02:34.350 --> 02:35.030
Let's go.

02:44.150 --> 02:45.079
Commandant Fan!

02:49.360 --> 02:50.310
You go ahead.

02:51.850 --> 02:52.430
Let's go.

02:57.700 --> 02:59.310
To call us sworn siblings just now

02:59.310 --> 03:00.770
was an expedient measure.

03:00.870 --> 03:02.310
People in the army gossip.

03:02.310 --> 03:03.560
If anything has offended you,

03:03.560 --> 03:05.220
please don't take it to heart.

03:05.310 --> 03:06.240
Not at all.

03:06.840 --> 03:09.440
I've always regarded you as a brother,
Lord Li.

03:09.650 --> 03:11.380
I'm just afraid I'm not worthy.

03:11.430 --> 03:12.240
After all,

03:12.470 --> 03:14.270
I haven't read many books on war,

03:14.560 --> 03:15.870
and I can barely read.

03:17.560 --> 03:19.630
A person's worth lies in their character,

03:19.630 --> 03:21.230
not in how well they can read.

03:21.840 --> 03:25.280
Then, greetings, Brother.

03:26.400 --> 03:27.600
Is that how you say it?

03:32.079 --> 03:33.340
I return the courtesy.

03:33.510 --> 03:34.710
That is how you say it.

03:35.360 --> 03:36.760
I shall take my leave now.

05:19.060 --> 05:24.420
[Pursuit of Jade]

05:24.520 --> 05:27.160
[Episode 32]

05:27.190 --> 05:30.880
[Qinwu Hall]

05:28.920 --> 05:31.070
This is simply outrageous!

05:31.630 --> 05:33.190
Even in the palace,

05:33.430 --> 05:35.920
we have never suffered such humiliation!

05:40.110 --> 05:41.170
What are you doing?

05:41.560 --> 05:43.490
You still expect me to drink?

05:43.720 --> 05:45.390
Hey! How many days has it been?

05:46.680 --> 05:48.830
The Marquis of Wu'an hasn't returned.

05:49.120 --> 05:51.380
And the Princess Royal refuses to see me.

05:51.680 --> 05:52.920
Let me tell you,

05:53.380 --> 05:54.270
if you people

05:54.270 --> 05:57.120
dare to keep me waiting here again today,

05:57.159 --> 05:59.800
I will return to the capital immediately.

05:59.830 --> 06:00.870
I will go before His Majesty

06:00.870 --> 06:03.070
and file a complaint against all of you!

06:05.040 --> 06:06.450
What is all this noise?

06:08.830 --> 06:12.000
Greetings, Your Highness.

06:13.710 --> 06:15.830
Your Highness cares for the soldiers.

06:15.830 --> 06:16.830
It's been so many days,

06:16.830 --> 06:19.310
yet you haven't found a moment to see me.

06:19.310 --> 06:21.400
It made me really upset.

06:21.630 --> 06:22.430
You may leave.

06:25.390 --> 06:27.310
I have been busy with affairs lately.

06:27.310 --> 06:28.630
It was hard to get away.

06:29.120 --> 06:31.120
I hope you understand, Head Eunuch.

06:32.000 --> 06:33.750
I wonder why you sought me out,

06:33.750 --> 06:35.010
and what the matter is.

06:35.190 --> 06:37.270
Your Highness has been away
from the palace for a long time.

06:37.270 --> 06:40.800
His Majesty and Consort Dowager An
miss you dearly.

06:40.800 --> 06:42.750
So they sent me here specially

06:42.750 --> 06:44.680
to visit Your Highness.

06:46.720 --> 06:48.450
Mother Consort and His Majesty

06:48.870 --> 06:51.600
knew about my coming
to the Northwest frontline,

06:51.870 --> 06:53.400
and yet they were not angry?

06:56.870 --> 06:58.800
Just speak your mind, Head Eunuch.

06:59.750 --> 07:01.880
Your Highness is indeed intelligent.

07:01.990 --> 07:04.160
Indeed. Before I came here,

07:04.160 --> 07:09.040
His Majesty and Consort Dowager An
had a message

07:09.040 --> 07:11.680
for me to specially pass on
to Your Highness.

07:12.920 --> 07:16.800
Now that the rebels
in Chongzhou have been quelled,

07:16.800 --> 07:19.040
and the whole country is celebrating,

07:19.510 --> 07:21.770
the marriage
between you and the marquis

07:21.800 --> 07:23.720
should happen sooner rather than later.

07:23.720 --> 07:24.680
What did you say?

07:26.000 --> 07:27.750
My marriage with whom?

07:29.190 --> 07:30.680
The Marquis of Wu'an.

07:31.360 --> 07:32.220
In your dreams!

07:34.120 --> 07:35.720
My brother is easily swayed.

07:36.159 --> 07:38.960
It must be you stupid servants
bringing up the past

07:38.970 --> 07:40.360
and fanning the flames,

07:40.360 --> 07:41.720
reminding him of this.

07:42.360 --> 07:43.560
I do not accept

07:43.950 --> 07:45.190
this marriage.

07:48.810 --> 07:51.390
Your Highness has been out of the palace
for less than half a year.

07:51.390 --> 07:54.830
How have you learned to curse now?

07:57.950 --> 07:59.870
The Marquis of Wu'an
has distinguished military service.

07:59.870 --> 08:03.390
He is truly an excellent match.

08:03.870 --> 08:04.750
Besides,

08:05.240 --> 08:07.970
this is His Majesty's decree.

08:08.100 --> 08:09.910
Could it be that Your Highness

08:10.330 --> 08:12.570
intends to disobey the decree?

08:24.430 --> 08:26.390
You should go discuss this marriage

08:26.390 --> 08:29.000
with the Marquis of Wu'an first.

08:29.840 --> 08:31.160
If he agrees to it,

08:31.850 --> 08:33.169
I will too.

08:35.390 --> 08:35.960
You...

08:36.210 --> 08:38.030
Of course, of course.

08:39.150 --> 08:41.340
I will handle it right away.

08:49.670 --> 08:51.530
Please pass the message, Eunuch.

08:52.440 --> 08:53.360
I

08:54.600 --> 08:56.460
thank my brother for his concern.

08:56.960 --> 08:59.630
I shall take my leave now.

09:09.390 --> 09:11.120
Finally, some relief.

09:18.080 --> 09:19.780
It's been so many days!

09:20.440 --> 09:21.670
Even if His Lordship is busy,

09:21.670 --> 09:24.530
he can't keep the Imperial Decree
waiting forever.

09:25.320 --> 09:28.320
This is a restricted military area.
Please stop here.

09:30.000 --> 09:31.240
Very well.

09:31.680 --> 09:34.530
Open your wretched eyes and look closely!

09:34.600 --> 09:36.670
I have an Imperial Decree!

09:38.550 --> 09:42.000
I'd like to see
who dares to stop me today!

09:43.740 --> 09:44.390
Go!

09:52.050 --> 09:52.870
-Halt!
-Halt!

09:55.200 --> 09:57.870
I know Your Lordship is busy
with official duties.

09:57.870 --> 09:59.410
But you haven't found time

09:59.630 --> 10:01.150
to see me

10:01.150 --> 10:03.360
these few days,

10:03.480 --> 10:04.320
leaving me with no choice

10:04.320 --> 10:06.810
but to bring this decree here

10:06.840 --> 10:10.320
to disturb you personally.

10:12.910 --> 10:13.630
Come in.

10:18.120 --> 10:18.580
Please.

10:27.120 --> 10:29.790
Greetings, Your Lordship.

10:33.670 --> 10:36.390
What important matter do you have,
Chief Eunuch,

10:36.390 --> 10:37.790
that to see me,

10:38.220 --> 10:40.680
you dare to trespass
into the military camp?

10:43.600 --> 10:44.600
Your Lordship,

10:44.670 --> 10:48.030
this is great joyous news.

10:50.880 --> 10:52.930
His Majesty has a decree.

10:58.030 --> 10:59.230
Marquis of Wu'an.

11:04.200 --> 11:07.470
Your Lordship may listen without kneeling.

11:08.600 --> 11:10.110
The Emperor proclaims:

11:10.240 --> 11:11.600
the heaven blesses our dynasty.

11:11.600 --> 11:14.410
Now that the Chongzhou rebels
have been wiped out,

11:14.910 --> 11:18.200
at this time of national celebration,

11:18.320 --> 11:21.150
the Princess Royal
and the Marquis of Wu'an

11:21.150 --> 11:24.320
-should get married sooner than later...
-No need to say more.

11:24.320 --> 11:26.250
Go back and tell that young emperor

11:26.790 --> 11:28.790
I had important duties to attend to,

11:28.870 --> 11:30.670
so the decree was not delivered.

11:31.000 --> 11:33.530
I will pretend
you never said anything today.

11:34.550 --> 11:35.870
Those of us who heard it

11:36.320 --> 11:37.960
won't breathe a word of it.

11:39.600 --> 11:43.430
I wouldn't dare
to deceive the sovereign like that.

11:44.160 --> 11:44.980
Besides,

11:45.510 --> 11:49.860
this is all His Majesty's deep favor
for Your Lordship.

11:49.960 --> 11:53.320
You just need to nod your head,

11:53.390 --> 11:55.550
and I can return to the capital

11:55.550 --> 11:57.790
to report back to His Majesty.

11:59.270 --> 12:00.600
And if I...

12:02.030 --> 12:03.440
refuse to nod?

12:05.200 --> 12:06.030
Refuse...

12:08.020 --> 12:08.880
Your Lordship.

12:09.440 --> 12:13.070
Does this mean
you intend to defy the decree?

12:13.870 --> 12:16.630
I wouldn't dare deceive the Emperor.

12:18.520 --> 12:19.700
Defy the decree?

12:27.000 --> 12:27.870
Your Lordship...

12:27.870 --> 12:30.270
Your Lordship, what are you trying to do?

12:35.910 --> 12:36.960
Your Lordship,

12:37.440 --> 12:38.680
do you really

12:39.120 --> 12:40.720
intend to rebel?

12:47.590 --> 12:49.590
The Xie family has served the Great Yin

12:49.590 --> 12:51.180
loyally for a century.

12:52.510 --> 12:54.640
My father was even honored as a martyr.

12:56.400 --> 12:59.000
I simply do not wish
to tarnish his reputation.

13:02.670 --> 13:04.670
Go back and tell that young emperor:

13:05.460 --> 13:08.060
if he no longer wishes
to sit on the throne anymore,

13:08.060 --> 13:10.720
I can easily find someone else
to take his place.

13:10.790 --> 13:12.150
Seventeen years ago,

13:12.480 --> 13:15.010
he ascended to the throne
with Wei Yan's help.

13:15.510 --> 13:16.630
And now,

13:17.720 --> 13:19.630
I can deprive him of that if I want.

13:21.150 --> 13:22.000
What?

13:22.550 --> 13:23.440
Your Lordship,

13:23.960 --> 13:26.890
do you realize
you are threatening His Majesty?

13:29.390 --> 13:31.670
Please don't kill me, Your Lordship!

13:31.670 --> 13:35.030
I am merely a messenger.

13:42.270 --> 13:44.240
I simply wish for harmony

13:44.510 --> 13:47.600
between the sovereign and his subject
with His Majesty.

13:47.600 --> 13:49.670
If you pass on the wrong message,

13:51.080 --> 13:53.540
you might jeopardize the nation's affairs.

13:54.550 --> 13:55.390
Thank you...

13:56.030 --> 13:58.960
Thank you for sparing my life,
Your Lordship!

14:09.840 --> 14:10.440
This...

14:10.440 --> 14:11.240
Take it away.

14:21.960 --> 14:22.630
Quick!

14:22.760 --> 14:23.380
Quick!

14:23.840 --> 14:25.750
That hurt!

14:27.570 --> 14:31.920
[Break the Enemy's Stronghold]

14:37.270 --> 14:39.120
Xie Jiuheng, oh, Xie Jiuheng.

14:39.790 --> 14:41.200
Eunuch Li came here

14:41.220 --> 14:42.600
on the Emperor's orders.

14:42.600 --> 14:44.200
You cut off one of his ears.

14:44.220 --> 14:46.270
Isn't that a slap in the Emperor's face?

14:46.270 --> 14:47.200
What do we do now?

14:47.910 --> 14:50.310
Are we turning against the Imperial Court?

14:51.160 --> 14:53.480
The little Emperor
is still under Wei Yan's thumb,

14:53.480 --> 14:54.870
acting dumb.

14:55.030 --> 14:56.830
He doesn't dare turn against me.

14:59.960 --> 15:02.000
Since the Emperor ascended the throne
as a child,

15:02.000 --> 15:04.360
Prime Minister Wei has been
usurping his power.

15:04.360 --> 15:04.840
Now,

15:04.840 --> 15:06.960
he must be desperate for power.

15:07.240 --> 15:09.360
I don't think he'll let this go.

15:09.960 --> 15:11.750
If he doesn't want the throne,

15:12.080 --> 15:14.340
I can find someone else to take his place.

15:14.720 --> 15:16.070
I happen to

15:17.030 --> 15:18.830
have plans to depose him anyway.

15:21.030 --> 15:21.960
Depose him?

15:23.240 --> 15:24.170
Are you serious?

15:32.000 --> 15:33.080
Although

15:33.630 --> 15:35.080
the Great Yin court

15:35.080 --> 15:36.550
is too corrupt to save,

15:37.000 --> 15:37.910
and I know

15:37.960 --> 15:40.360
you won't serve such an incompetent ruler,

15:40.360 --> 15:41.100
now,

15:41.870 --> 15:43.550
if we support the Imperial Great-Grandson,

15:43.550 --> 15:44.630
in a dozen years,

15:44.670 --> 15:45.790
who's to say

15:45.810 --> 15:48.070
Yu Bao'er won't become another Qi Sheng?

15:52.270 --> 15:54.000
I don't know

15:54.440 --> 15:55.970
what Yu Bao'er will become,

15:56.320 --> 15:58.880
but I will never become another Wei Yan.

16:02.200 --> 16:03.080
Fine.

16:03.770 --> 16:04.370
By the way,

16:05.030 --> 16:07.030
aren't you going back
to Jizhou Prefecture?

16:07.030 --> 16:07.910
Why should I?

16:09.840 --> 16:11.120
That Li Huai'an

16:11.120 --> 16:13.440
visits Mrs. Fan every other day.

16:13.440 --> 16:14.970
Are you really not worried?

16:19.270 --> 16:20.730
Don't look at me like that.

16:21.160 --> 16:22.600
They are already calling each other
brother and sister,

16:22.600 --> 16:23.720
getting all cozy.

16:23.720 --> 16:26.600
He'll swoop in when she's vulnerable.

16:26.750 --> 16:28.810
-Such low-level courting—
-Enough.

16:28.810 --> 16:29.970
And you're not low-level?

16:29.970 --> 16:30.510
I...

16:30.750 --> 16:32.080
Mind your own business.

16:32.190 --> 16:32.830
Report!

16:34.550 --> 16:35.270
My Lord,

16:35.890 --> 16:37.270
the rebel remnant from Chongzhou,

16:37.270 --> 16:38.870
Sui Yuanqing, is attacking!

16:46.510 --> 16:47.630
How many are their troops?

16:47.630 --> 16:49.000
Only a few dozen soldiers.

16:49.000 --> 16:50.270
They stormed the gate recklessly.

16:50.270 --> 16:51.670
There are no reinforcements behind them.

16:51.670 --> 16:52.400
It looks like

16:52.480 --> 16:53.880
a suicide mission.

17:01.080 --> 17:02.240
Xie Zheng!

17:03.150 --> 17:05.589
Come out, you coward!

17:06.680 --> 17:08.079
Today, we settle

17:08.200 --> 17:09.550
our scores!

17:27.730 --> 17:29.530
Why bother, Heir Apparent Sui?

17:30.160 --> 17:31.790
Why come here just to die?

17:34.920 --> 17:36.790
Stop your fake mercy!

17:37.180 --> 17:39.290
You and Fan Changyu killed my father.

17:40.310 --> 17:41.510
If I don't avenge him,

17:42.310 --> 17:43.870
I'm not human!

17:44.750 --> 17:46.200
Die!

18:03.380 --> 18:08.050
[Chongzhou]

18:08.590 --> 18:10.270
If he believes it, let it be.

18:10.590 --> 18:11.480
If not,

18:12.640 --> 18:14.720
even if you have to destroy
the Eastern Palace seal on the spot,

18:14.720 --> 18:17.070
it must never
fall into anyone else's hands.

18:17.070 --> 18:18.330
Rest assured, Master.

18:23.950 --> 18:26.180
[Lord Changxin's Wife, Lady Yin]

18:28.820 --> 18:29.530
Mother?

18:36.100 --> 18:37.760
Why have you come so suddenly—

18:38.310 --> 18:40.570
Why did you treat your brother like that?

18:44.140 --> 18:45.310
Yuanqing said

18:46.040 --> 18:47.500
he wants to avenge Father.

18:48.270 --> 18:49.470
This is filial piety,

18:49.560 --> 18:50.930
and I cannot stop him.

18:51.070 --> 18:52.200
Filial piety?

18:52.610 --> 18:55.470
Then why didn't you
go and fulfill your filial duty?

18:56.280 --> 18:58.810
I have to stay here
to take care of you, Mother.

18:59.550 --> 19:01.070
You knew fully well
that the Marquis of Wu'an

19:01.070 --> 19:03.200
is hunting all of you down everywhere.

19:03.350 --> 19:05.560
Yet you incited Qing'er
to avenge your father.

19:05.560 --> 19:06.760
You are so vicious!

19:14.160 --> 19:16.230
Father never liked me.

19:17.830 --> 19:19.270
Actually, deep down,

19:20.210 --> 19:22.210
you prefer Yuanqing too, don't you?

19:22.690 --> 19:23.650
He is my son.

19:24.360 --> 19:25.890
Of course I prefer him.

19:31.310 --> 19:32.030
Mother,

19:33.640 --> 19:35.190
what do you mean by that?

19:35.920 --> 19:36.960
In this world,

19:38.400 --> 19:39.750
how could a mother not recognize

19:39.750 --> 19:41.160
her own flesh and blood?

19:44.920 --> 19:47.160
I brought you back

19:47.920 --> 19:49.450
from that fire 17 years ago.

19:51.750 --> 19:52.750
At first,

19:53.960 --> 19:55.400
seeing you injured beyond recognition

19:55.400 --> 19:56.510
broke my heart.

19:58.150 --> 19:59.980
But when I found out you weren't Yuanhuai,

19:59.980 --> 20:01.510
it broke my heart even more.

20:06.500 --> 20:07.850
So you knew all along.

20:12.310 --> 20:13.270
Then, Mother,

20:13.920 --> 20:16.310
why didn't you expose me
right then and there?

20:16.310 --> 20:17.160
Back then,

20:18.110 --> 20:19.790
you were just a small child.

20:21.240 --> 20:24.500
You were disfigured
by the Crown Princess just to survive.

20:25.090 --> 20:27.470
When you were recovering
in Lord Changxin's Mansion,

20:27.470 --> 20:29.510
you were so pitiful,

20:30.000 --> 20:32.190
crying out for your mother every day.

20:33.050 --> 20:35.210
My heart softened listening to you.

20:36.480 --> 20:37.080
I thought,

20:38.440 --> 20:40.550
since Heaven
let you live in my son's place,

20:40.550 --> 20:42.480
I should let you live a good life—

20:44.550 --> 20:49.210
consider it an act of accumulating virtue
for my poor Yuanhuai who died wrongfully.

20:49.830 --> 20:51.440
But I was wrong.

20:52.510 --> 20:54.750
I thought you were just a stray dog.

20:54.750 --> 20:57.210
I never imagined
you would be a vicious wolf!

20:58.110 --> 20:59.770
My biggest regret in this life

21:00.480 --> 21:02.070
is taking a rebel as my son,

21:02.880 --> 21:04.940
and being a mother to a viper like you!

21:15.000 --> 21:20.720
I am Qi Min, the Imperial Grandson
of the Eastern Palace.

21:28.270 --> 21:29.800
Isn't it a good thing

21:32.030 --> 21:33.040
to be my mother?

21:38.310 --> 21:39.640
Yuanqing and Yuanhuai

21:40.440 --> 21:42.110
are my only sons.

21:44.140 --> 21:45.010
Who...

21:45.830 --> 21:47.030
do you think you are!

22:27.070 --> 22:29.790
Don't think that
just because you treated me well,

22:29.790 --> 22:31.480
I wouldn't dare to kill you.

22:36.200 --> 22:38.640
I-I gave you a chance.

22:41.750 --> 22:43.200
But don't worry.

22:44.440 --> 22:47.960
Xie Zheng will soon send Sui Yuanqing

22:48.240 --> 22:50.110
to serve you in the afterlife.

23:18.440 --> 23:19.920
Bring her body.

23:20.170 --> 23:21.230
It's still useful.

23:21.240 --> 23:21.850
Yes.

23:30.950 --> 23:34.030
[Peace at the border]

23:40.920 --> 23:41.550
Come in.

23:47.240 --> 23:47.720
Fan.

23:48.590 --> 23:49.720
Your husband
is going to be the Prince Consort.

23:49.720 --> 23:50.640
Is it true?

23:53.340 --> 23:55.160
Wasn't Li Menkan the one who's supposed
to marry the princess?

23:55.160 --> 23:56.400
They can switch the groom
at the last minute

23:56.400 --> 23:58.720
for an event
as big as marrying a princess?

23:58.720 --> 24:00.450
I don't want to talk about this.

24:04.850 --> 24:05.540
All right.

24:11.880 --> 24:12.750
I have news about Sui Yuanhuai,

24:12.750 --> 24:13.960
whom you asked me

24:13.960 --> 24:14.790
to look into.

24:16.350 --> 24:17.720
They say tonight,

24:17.720 --> 24:19.240
a large number of troops
will be dispatched.

24:19.240 --> 24:20.440
I reckon it's a massive manhunt

24:20.440 --> 24:21.860
for that scoundrel.

24:22.720 --> 24:24.920
That scoundrel is very cunning.

24:25.590 --> 24:27.500
He's sneakier than a fox or a weasel.

24:27.500 --> 24:28.900
Before, your husband...

24:31.710 --> 24:33.630
Th-The Marquis of Wu'an's troops

24:34.310 --> 24:36.170
were fooled by him several times.

24:38.680 --> 24:40.140
He is muddying the waters.

24:41.200 --> 24:43.240
He wants to wait
until we're exhausted from searching

24:43.240 --> 24:45.170
before finding a chance to escape.

24:48.030 --> 24:50.650
So he is the son
of the former Crown Prince?

24:50.720 --> 24:51.440
He...

24:52.910 --> 24:54.640
He could have been the Emperor?

24:55.720 --> 24:57.580
He could be in line for the throne.

25:00.440 --> 25:02.550
But for someone so noble,

25:03.680 --> 25:06.110
why would he impersonate Sui Yuanhuai?

25:07.110 --> 25:08.680
Isn't this common
in the shadow puppet shows

25:08.680 --> 25:09.720
you watch?

25:09.950 --> 25:11.400
Those nobles and aristocrats

25:11.400 --> 25:12.930
fight and snatch every day.

25:13.350 --> 25:14.920
It's nothing but greed for the throne

25:14.920 --> 25:17.250
and the sordid schemes of imperial power.

25:23.790 --> 25:25.390
Fan, what are you looking at?

25:27.070 --> 25:29.000
Qianqian seemed to have mentioned

25:29.070 --> 25:30.960
that he is extremely afraid of fire.

25:30.960 --> 25:33.020
He doesn't even light lamps at night.

25:36.890 --> 25:38.880
If that's the case,

25:40.060 --> 25:41.770
we can look for

25:42.000 --> 25:43.990
houses that remain pitch black

25:44.680 --> 25:46.470
at an hour where they should be lit up.

25:46.470 --> 25:46.920
That way,

25:46.920 --> 25:49.090
we can narrow down our search area.

25:49.240 --> 25:50.840
Why are you so fixated on him?

25:51.000 --> 25:52.890
Just to vent anger for Manager Yu?

25:55.110 --> 25:56.310
You don't understand.

25:56.310 --> 25:57.200
He...

25:59.650 --> 26:01.710
might be involved in something huge.

26:02.400 --> 26:04.510
He once showed me a Tiger Tally.

26:04.920 --> 26:07.200
They say it's related
to the Jinzhou Massacre years ago.

26:07.200 --> 26:09.200
It has something to do with Jinzhou?

26:12.070 --> 26:14.000
Yan Zheng must be eager to catch him

26:14.110 --> 26:15.770
to get some answers out of him.

26:16.500 --> 26:17.830
Go get my command token.

26:18.200 --> 26:19.720
Tell them
there's an arrest operation tonight.

26:19.720 --> 26:21.780
It's a good chance to drill our squad.

26:22.500 --> 26:23.100
Got it.

26:55.790 --> 26:58.050
There's someone inside. Surround them.

27:24.200 --> 27:25.380
His throat was slit.

27:25.560 --> 27:27.420
Looks like he's been dead a while.

27:28.200 --> 27:29.540
How can he be dead?

27:32.110 --> 27:33.040
Keep searching.

27:33.160 --> 27:34.960
Check the body for a Tiger Tally.

27:35.750 --> 27:36.790
A Tiger what?

27:37.480 --> 27:39.110
Tiger Tally. Like in the operas.

27:39.110 --> 27:40.110
Just hurry up and look.

27:40.110 --> 27:40.790
Okay.

28:10.880 --> 28:12.200
General Fan Changyu reporting.

28:12.200 --> 28:13.730
Greetings, Your Lordship.

28:15.640 --> 28:18.840
I, Jin Changsheng,
pay my respects to the Prince Consort.

28:19.200 --> 28:20.480
One more word of nonsense,

28:20.480 --> 28:22.340
and I'll send you to the Mess Crew.

28:22.650 --> 28:23.860
Yes, Prince Consort.

28:24.750 --> 28:27.030
I'll go right now, Prince Consort.

28:37.480 --> 28:38.740
Sui Yuanhuai is dead.

28:39.750 --> 28:40.750
This lead

28:41.550 --> 28:42.350
has gone cold.

28:55.310 --> 28:57.220
Sui Yuanhuai died just like that?

29:07.590 --> 29:09.650
It looks very much like Sui Yuanhuai.

29:11.350 --> 29:12.480
All the evidence

29:13.270 --> 29:15.070
shows that he's dead.

29:16.400 --> 29:19.510
But the more evidence there is,
the more suspicious it gets.

29:19.510 --> 29:21.710
Have Zhao Xun
come identify the body himself.

29:21.710 --> 29:22.880
But no matter what,

29:22.900 --> 29:23.750
Sui Yuanhui

29:23.770 --> 29:25.500
no longer exists in this world.

29:34.330 --> 29:36.280
There have been rumors for years

29:36.550 --> 29:39.200
that Wei Yan had orders to hold
the Tiger Tally to get reinforcements

29:39.200 --> 29:40.800
to lift the siege of Jinzhou.

29:41.200 --> 29:43.830
But he suddenly turned back
to the Capital midway,

29:43.830 --> 29:45.030
delaying the rescue.

29:47.680 --> 29:49.310
Back then,
when Wei Qilin was transporting grain,

29:49.310 --> 29:51.510
he suddenly changed course to Chongzhou.

29:51.510 --> 29:53.240
It must have been Wei Yan ordering him
to use the Tiger Tally

29:53.240 --> 29:55.100
to mobilize troops in Chongzhou.

29:56.270 --> 29:57.590
But in the end,

29:57.590 --> 29:59.440
the Lord Changxin neither sent troops,

29:59.440 --> 30:01.370
nor did he prevent the grain delay,

30:01.440 --> 30:02.680
yet no one knew why.

30:09.080 --> 30:11.640
If Lord Changxin
saw the Tiger Tally back then,

30:11.640 --> 30:12.680
but claimed it was fake

30:12.680 --> 30:14.210
and refused to send troops,

30:16.200 --> 30:17.270
then that means

30:17.720 --> 30:19.510
Wei Qilin was truly wronged.

30:21.880 --> 30:22.880
It seems...

30:24.560 --> 30:26.780
we are getting closer to the truth

30:28.110 --> 30:29.510
of the Jinzhou Massacre.

30:29.680 --> 30:31.740
If only we could find the Tiger Tally.

30:32.430 --> 30:34.440
I even searched
Lord Changxin's belongings,

30:34.440 --> 30:36.900
and the items
Sui Yuanqing carried with him,

30:36.920 --> 30:37.980
but found nothing.

30:38.160 --> 30:39.240
That Sui Yuanqing—

30:39.240 --> 30:40.110
he'd rather be tortured

30:40.110 --> 30:41.830
than reveal the whereabouts
of the Tiger Tally.

30:41.830 --> 30:43.630
He even had the energy to mock me.

30:44.070 --> 30:46.350
I should have let Mrs. Fan chop him up.

30:53.680 --> 30:54.540
Your Lordship.

30:55.750 --> 30:57.680
I arranged
for Zhao Xun to examine the body.

30:57.680 --> 30:58.680
As you predicted,

30:58.960 --> 31:00.550
the deceased is not Sui Yuanhuai.

31:00.550 --> 31:03.110
It is a double
raised by the Lan family since childhood.

31:03.110 --> 31:05.200
Not only does the double look identical,

31:05.200 --> 31:06.830
but every burn mark on his body

31:06.830 --> 31:08.560
was meticulously replicated.

31:08.640 --> 31:10.550
What about the identity of the woman

31:10.550 --> 31:11.750
who died in the manor?

31:12.160 --> 31:13.400
Zhao Xun identified her.

31:13.400 --> 31:15.530
It is indeed the Lord Changxin's wife.

31:19.310 --> 31:20.620
To save himself,

31:21.110 --> 31:23.550
he didn't hesitate
to even kill his adoptive mother.

31:23.550 --> 31:25.030
To catch Suiyuan—

31:25.480 --> 31:26.160
no—

31:26.920 --> 31:28.980
it's time to call him by his real name.

31:30.000 --> 31:31.350
To catch Qi Min,

31:31.920 --> 31:33.590
we need other leads.

31:34.510 --> 31:35.570
Are there any more?

31:37.310 --> 31:38.570
All the leads are dead.

31:39.480 --> 31:40.780
It is strange.

31:40.830 --> 31:42.290
We've surrounded them several times,

31:42.290 --> 31:44.420
but they always seemed to be prepared.

31:44.680 --> 31:45.720
I suspect

31:46.130 --> 31:48.330
he has spies within the Command Office.

31:54.110 --> 31:54.920
It seems

31:55.240 --> 31:57.030
someone is being used as a pawn

31:57.050 --> 31:59.510
while thinking they are upholding justice.

32:00.720 --> 32:01.580
Your Lordship,

32:01.880 --> 32:03.140
what should we do next?

32:05.050 --> 32:06.910
Take Zhao Xun to see Sui Yuanqing.

32:07.240 --> 32:08.910
Inform him of Lord Changxin's wife's

32:08.910 --> 32:09.710
death.

32:11.840 --> 32:12.880
Squad One, to the left.

32:12.880 --> 32:14.210
Squad Two, to the right.

32:14.510 --> 32:15.960
Spread out on both sides.

32:16.110 --> 32:16.770
-Yes!
-Yes!

32:17.480 --> 32:18.680
Check the grass and crevices.

32:18.680 --> 32:19.400
Understood!

32:19.400 --> 32:20.530
Search everywhere.

32:20.680 --> 32:21.350
Leave no stone unturned.

32:21.350 --> 32:21.680
Go!

32:21.680 --> 32:22.340
Check here.

32:24.350 --> 32:25.150
Nothing here.

32:25.550 --> 32:26.240
Over there.

32:26.960 --> 32:27.560
Follow me!

32:30.750 --> 32:32.590
Master, it's the Xie Army.

32:35.780 --> 32:37.710
Sui Yuanqing alone wasn't enough.

32:38.680 --> 32:40.280
It seems the Marquis of Wu'an

32:40.600 --> 32:43.000
won't rest until he has my head.

32:44.510 --> 32:45.910
Any news on Her Ladyship?

32:46.680 --> 32:47.880
Still no sign of her.

32:57.400 --> 32:58.110
Master.

32:58.550 --> 33:00.200
The Li family took so much from us,

33:00.200 --> 33:02.130
yet there's no sign of our contact.

33:02.160 --> 33:04.270
They let the Marquis of Wu'an corner us.

33:04.270 --> 33:05.530
Have they turned on us?

33:07.790 --> 33:09.550
If the Li family had turned on us,

33:09.550 --> 33:11.610
we would have been captured long ago.

33:12.750 --> 33:15.750
But though I heard
they are grandfather and grandson,

33:16.770 --> 33:19.090
Grand Tutor Li and Li Huai'an

33:19.350 --> 33:21.410
are truly people on different paths.

33:27.780 --> 33:28.920
It's about time.

33:29.180 --> 33:30.510
He should be here by now.

33:31.000 --> 33:32.510
That is if he believed me.

33:37.110 --> 33:37.640
Master.

33:46.770 --> 33:48.580
I'm very pleased

33:48.900 --> 33:51.090
to get your help, Grand Tutor Li.

34:28.590 --> 34:29.670
I have something to tell you.

34:29.670 --> 34:30.929
I don't want to hear it.

34:31.070 --> 34:32.270
I just want to tell you

34:34.190 --> 34:36.969
that anyone in this world
can become the Prince Consort,

34:36.969 --> 34:38.380
except for me, Xie Zheng.

34:40.800 --> 34:42.590
I have already married into your family.

34:42.590 --> 34:44.719
I can only belong to Fan Changyu alone.

34:46.130 --> 34:47.250
I'll only love you

34:48.920 --> 34:49.960
in this lifetime.

35:14.360 --> 35:15.030
Stop...

35:19.230 --> 35:21.090
Stop being so nice to me, will you?

35:21.880 --> 35:23.210
The better you treat me,

35:24.880 --> 35:26.140
the more uneasy I feel.

35:27.810 --> 35:29.470
Is it because of your origins?

35:31.970 --> 35:32.970
You know about it?

35:35.880 --> 35:45.940
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

35:40.480 --> 35:41.630
I read that letter.

35:42.550 --> 35:44.180
I know he's your father.

35:45.550 --> 35:46.920
And I also know what you're afraid of.

35:46.670 --> 35:56.220
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

35:48.590 --> 35:50.240
But what I want to tell you is,

35:51.070 --> 35:52.590
I will keep investigating

35:53.920 --> 35:55.580
until I get to the bottom of it.

35:57.360 --> 35:58.590
I want to be with you

35:57.420 --> 36:01.900
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

36:00.030 --> 36:01.260
on this path.

36:01.920 --> 36:06.880
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

36:07.560 --> 36:09.740
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

36:10.070 --> 36:14.720
♪ I find her there ♪

36:15.230 --> 36:16.920
But Sui Yuanhuai is already dead.

36:16.220 --> 36:25.850
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

36:17.620 --> 36:18.830
What if the truth

36:19.150 --> 36:20.920
isn't what we think?

36:29.510 --> 36:30.840
This is the second thing

36:31.670 --> 36:32.920
I want to tell you.

36:33.800 --> 36:34.710
I plan

36:37.110 --> 36:38.510
to release Sui Yuanqing.

36:38.920 --> 36:39.670
What?

36:56.630 --> 36:57.320
Leave us.

36:57.880 --> 36:58.440
Yes.

37:03.510 --> 37:04.370
Heir Apparent.

37:05.320 --> 37:06.630
Zhao Xun?

37:07.500 --> 37:08.830
You traitor!

37:08.880 --> 37:10.210
You betrayed Yuanhuai!

37:12.150 --> 37:13.010
Heir Apparent.

37:13.840 --> 37:15.800
It was Yuanhuai who betrayed you.

37:19.590 --> 37:20.840
A traitor,

37:22.110 --> 37:24.360
seeing that Yuanhuai has escaped,

37:25.000 --> 37:27.550
wants to extract a confession
for the Marquis of Wu'an,

37:27.550 --> 37:29.680
and drive a wedge between us brothers.

37:30.710 --> 37:32.430
Save your breath.

37:33.360 --> 37:35.110
Even if I can't kill you today,

37:37.070 --> 37:39.330
Yuanhuai will avenge me sooner or later.

37:41.960 --> 37:43.440
And who will avenge

37:43.440 --> 37:45.170
Lord Changxin's wife's death?

37:49.920 --> 37:51.000
Mother is dead?

37:56.320 --> 37:57.440
Marquis of Wu'an!

37:58.110 --> 37:59.670
What kind of hero are you,

38:00.000 --> 38:02.050
laying hands on a woman?

38:02.800 --> 38:05.330
It wasn't the Marquis of Wu'an
who killed her.

38:05.360 --> 38:06.490
It was Sui Yuanhuai.

38:07.110 --> 38:07.550
No.

38:08.550 --> 38:10.190
Or rather, it was Qi Min.

38:13.920 --> 38:14.670
Who?

38:15.390 --> 38:16.440
The dear brother

38:16.920 --> 38:18.480
by your side all these years

38:18.920 --> 38:20.190
is not Sui Yuanhuai,

38:20.810 --> 38:21.960
but Qi Min.

38:22.710 --> 38:27.280
He is the former Imperial Grandson of the Eastern Palace,
whom Lord Changxin helped harm.

38:27.280 --> 38:28.820
The real Sui Yuanhuai

38:29.230 --> 38:31.030
died in the fire at the Eastern Palace

38:31.030 --> 38:32.880
17 years ago.

38:41.800 --> 38:42.480
No...

38:45.800 --> 38:46.660
Impossible...

38:50.550 --> 38:52.280
You just want to use me

38:52.710 --> 38:54.040
to deal with my brother.

38:54.920 --> 38:56.000
Your Highness.

38:56.880 --> 38:57.910
Wake up.

38:59.000 --> 39:00.930
Qi Min killed the Princess Consort

39:00.960 --> 39:02.760
to fake his death and escape.

39:06.360 --> 39:09.560
He has now resumed
his identity as the Imperial Grandson.

39:09.710 --> 39:13.320
He is Qi Min,
who destroyed Lord Changxin's Mansion.

39:18.110 --> 39:18.760
No...

39:20.230 --> 39:21.290
That's not true...

39:22.280 --> 39:23.220
That's not true.

39:26.760 --> 39:28.740
Aren't you my brother's lackey?

39:30.030 --> 39:31.560
Why are you telling me this?

39:32.030 --> 39:32.830
That's right.

39:33.880 --> 39:35.590
I used to follow Qi Min.

39:36.920 --> 39:40.000
But that was for the legitimacy
of the previous dynasty.

39:40.000 --> 39:41.440
He is cruel by nature,

39:41.920 --> 39:43.720
and unfit to inherit the throne.

39:44.800 --> 39:46.200
That is why I had no choice

39:47.510 --> 39:49.570
but to defect to the Marquis of Wu'an.

40:00.150 --> 40:01.470
Sui Yuanhuai!

40:02.590 --> 40:03.190
No...

40:04.230 --> 40:05.440
Qi Min...

40:06.320 --> 40:08.350
I will tear you to pieces

40:08.960 --> 40:11.110
and avenge my father and mother!

40:14.710 --> 40:15.570
Your Highness.

40:16.630 --> 40:17.630
I can let you go.

40:19.190 --> 40:19.880
Let me go?

40:21.110 --> 40:21.840
Why?

40:22.440 --> 40:23.570
My mother, Lady Lan,

40:24.760 --> 40:26.210
raised Qi Min for years,

40:27.150 --> 40:28.550
yet she died at his hands.

40:30.800 --> 40:32.570
I only hate that I am powerless.

40:33.030 --> 40:34.840
If you can get rid of Qi Min,

40:35.400 --> 40:37.590
we will both be avenged.

40:45.670 --> 40:47.670
Although you are just a lackey,

40:52.110 --> 40:53.550
as long as you let me go,

40:55.320 --> 40:57.070
I will grant your wish.

41:07.210 --> 41:08.610
Your Highness, this way.

41:18.480 --> 41:21.030
Can he really find Qi Min?

41:23.710 --> 41:25.970
They've been brothers for so many years.

41:26.110 --> 41:27.230
He'll have a way.

41:28.880 --> 41:31.500
[19th day of the 7th month,
in the 17th year of Zhengping]

41:43.030 --> 41:45.440
Sui Yuanqing escaped from prison.

41:46.000 --> 41:46.670
What?

41:51.150 --> 41:52.480
Deliver this
to the courier officer immediately.

41:52.480 --> 41:53.320
Send it to the Capital at once.

41:53.320 --> 41:54.070
It must be delivered!

41:54.070 --> 41:54.600
Yes, Sir.

42:09.970 --> 42:12.360
[The Government Office]
